2002-12-25  Markus Schwab  <g17m0@lycos.com>

	* ChangeLog: Changes of V0.6.02 commented
	
	* doc/Makefile.am: Remaining X-windows docus added

	* po/de.po, po/en.po, po/es.po: Only line-numbers actualized

	* X-windows/XPrintDlg.h, X-windows/XPrintDlg.cpp: Comments improved

	* Common/Parse.cpp:
	  Made freeBuffer more error-tolerant

	* Common/File.h, Common/DirSrch.h:
	  Undefining macros for dirent before defining them

	* gzo-cfg.h.in: HAVE_GTKMM added

	* README.windows: Updated

	* README: Minor changes

	* Makefile.am: Windows .def-file removed from the distribution

	* doc/index.html: Name of XPrintDialog corrected

